{"article_id":"1P8QYJMpH9qd8g72","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama will officially announce new executive actions on gun control from the White House Tuesday ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"but released details","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"about what to expect Monday evening .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Here is a portion of what has been released ,","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"you can read the rest at WhiteHouse.","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"gov :","depth":2},{"id":6,"text":"1 . Keep guns out of the wrong hands through background checks .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"The Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"( ATF )","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"is making clear","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that it doesn ' t matter where you conduct your business-from a store , at gun shows , or over the Internet :","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"If you ' re in the business","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"of selling firearms ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"you must get a license","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and conduct background checks .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"ATF is finalizing a rule","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to require background checks for people","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"trying to buy some of the most dangerous weapons and other items through a trust , corporation , or other legal entity .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Attorney General Loretta E. Lynch has sent a letter to States","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"highlighting the importance","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"of receiving complete criminal history .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The Attorney General convened a call with U.S . Attorneys around the country","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to direct federal prosecutors to continue to focus on smart and effective enforcement of our gun laws .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The President ' s FY2017 budget will include funding for 200 new ATF agents and investigators","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to help enforce our gun laws .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"3 . Increase mental health treatment and reporting to the background check system .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"The Administration is proposing a new $ 500 million investment","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to increase access to mental health care .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"The Social Security Administration has indicated","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that it will begin the rulemaking process","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"to include information in the background check system about beneficiaries","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"who are prohibited from possessing a firearm for mental health reasons .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The President has directed the Departments of Defense , Justice , and Homeland Security to conduct or sponsor research into gun safety technology .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"The President has also directed the departments to review the availability of smart gun technology on a regular basis ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"and to explore potential ways","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to further its use and development","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to more broadly improve gun safety .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"BREAKING :","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"This is not new !","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"https : //t.co/oiDHSeu76I","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"- Katie Pavlich","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"( @ KatiePavlich )","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"January 5 , 2016","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Fact :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Justice Department reports","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"less than 1 % of criminals got guns from # gunshowloophole","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"- in my book pic.","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"twitter.com/pkuECB9OZM","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"- Emily Miller","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( @ EmilyMiller )","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"January 4 , 2016","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"White House says","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"30,000 annual `` gun deaths . ''","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"FACT :","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"FBI says","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"8,124 homicides by gun .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"CDC cites","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"21,175 suicide by gun .","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"- Emily Miller","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"( @ EmilyMiller )","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"January 4 , 2016","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"You have n't strengthened anything .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"You 've restated existing law .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"Is # StopGunViolence dumb enough","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"to buy this ?","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"https : //t.co/oeYGCify9T","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"- Bob Owens","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"( @ bob_owens )","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"January 5 , 2016","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Gun control groups sure are easy to please .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"If I were them","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"I ' d be yelling","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"@ POTUS was blowing smoke ,","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"because he is .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"https : //t.co/HjROZZhA4l","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"- Sebastian","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"( @ SebastianSNBQ )","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"January 5 , 2016","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":82,"right":154,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":82,"left":80,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":79,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":5,"right":153,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":100,"right":152,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":6,"right":99,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":92,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":89,"right":91,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN